adminIlmiRegTable.name: adminIlmiRegTable
adminIlmiRegTable.description: The table implemented by the IME on the network side of the ATM UNI port contains all of the services that are available to the user-side IME indexed by service identifier.

adminIlmiRegEntry.name: adminIlmiRegEntry
adminIlmiRegEntry.description: Information about a single service provider that is available to the user-side IME.

adminIlmiRegPort.name: adminIlmiRegPort
adminIlmiRegPort.description: The value of 0 which has the special meaning of identifying the ATM Interface over which this message was received.

adminIlmiRegServiceID.name: adminIlmiRegServiceID
adminIlmiRegServiceID.description: This is the service identifier which uniquely identifies the type of service at the address provided in the table.

adminIlmiRegATMAddress.name: adminIlmiRegATMAddress
adminIlmiRegATMAddress.description: This is the full address of the service. The user-side IME may use this address to establish a connection with the service.

adminIlmiRegAddressIndex.name: adminIlmiRegAddressIndex
adminIlmiRegAddressIndex.description: An arbitrary integer to differentiate multiple rows containing different ATM addresses for the same service on the same port.

adminIlmiRegParm1.name: adminIlmiRegParm1
adminIlmiRegParm1.description: An octet string whose size and meaning is determined by the value of adminIlmiRegServiceID.
